OL,3,CMartyn's Law laid before parliament
OL,5,FThe mother of Manchester arena victim
OL,6,FMartyn Hett has welcomed the
OL,7,Fintroduction of Martyn's Law to
OL,8,Fparliament today.
OL,10,FThe measures, introduced to Parliament
OL,11,Fas a response to the attack on the
OL,12,FAriane Grande concert in May 2017, aim
OL,13,Fto create tighter security at public
OL,14,Fvenues, after Martyn and 21 other
OL,15,Fpeople were killed in a terror attack
OL,16,Fat the Manchester Arena in 2017.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
