OL,3,CMartyn's Law laid before parliament
OL,5,FThis includes improving security
OL,6,Fagainst terror threats, providing
OL,7,Fstaff with free online training
OL,8,Fprovided by the government, and a
OL,9,Frequirement that all venues have a
OL,10,Fcounter-terrorism plan.
OL,12,FUnder the proposals, there will be
OL,13,Fdifferent requirements for premises,
OL,14,Fbased on the number of people they can
OL,15,Fhold.
OL,17,FVenues with a capacity of between 100
OL,18,Fand 799 will be considered 'standard
OL,19,Ftier', and those with a higher
OL,20,Fcapacity of 800 will be classed as an
OL,21,F'enhanced tier'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
