OL,3,CMartyn's Law laid before parliament
OL,5,FWithin 'standard tier', venues will
OL,6,Fneed to undertake low-cost effective
OL,7,Fmeasures such as training, information
OL,8,Fsharing, and completion of a
OL,9,Fpreparedness plan.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, 'enhanced tier' premises
OL,12,Fwill be required to undertake an
OL,13,Fadditional risk assessment that will
OL,14,Finform the development and
OL,15,Fimplementation of a thorough security
OL,16,Fplan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
