OL,3,CMartyn's Law laid before parliament
OL,5,FFigen has been campaigning for the
OL,6,Fintroduction of Martyn's Law for the
OL,7,Fpast five years and in May 2024, she
OL,8,Fwalked 200 miles to Downing Street
OL,9,Fwhere she met with Sir Keir Starmer
OL,10,Fand Yvette Cooper as well as former
OL,11,Fprime minister Rishi Sunak the day the
OL,12,Felection was called.
OL,14,FThe now Prime Minister has committed
OL,15,Fto making Martyn's Law a priority and
OL,16,Fthe bill was included in the Labour
OL,17,Fgovernment's King's Speech.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
